==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Substantively
<hw>Sub"stan*tive*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a
substantive manner; in substance; essentially.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Gram.)</fld> <def>As a substantive, name, or noun;
<as>as, an adjective may be used <ex>substantively</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Substantiveness</ent>⟦br⟧
